OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FCovid: Some learners face  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25F10-month wait for driving  
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Ftest                       
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Some learners are waiting 10 months for
OL,6, a driving test while others face       
OL,7, eight-hour round trips for theirs due a
OL,8, shortage of examiners and instructors. 
OL,10,FThe shortage, coupled with the number  
OL,11,Fof learners who could not have lessons 
OL,12,For practical tests due to Covid rules  
OL,13,For lockdowns, has left a backlog.      
OL,15,FAbout 1.6 million UK learners had their
OL,16,Ftests every year before the pandemic,  
OL,17,Fbut that dropped to 436,000 in 2020-21.
OL,19,FThe department responsible for driving 
OL,20,Ftests is trying recruit 300 examiners. 
